EX_001.name: Scapular Wall Slides

en.name: Scapular Wall Slides
en.description: A shoulder mobility exercise targeting scapular control and upward rotation
instructions: Stand with your back flat against a wall
Place arms against wall in 'goalpost' position (90° shoulder abduction, 90° elbow flexion)
Slowly slide arms up the wall, maintaining contact throughout
Reach as high as comfortable without losing wall contact
Slowly lower back to starting position
cues: Keep lower back pressed against wall

functional_goals: Improve overhead reaching for daily activities
Improve shoulder mobility for self-care tasks

en.description: Core stability exercise with anti-extension focus

functional_goals: Enhance trunk control during daily activities

EX_544.name: Pendulum Exercises
EX_544.description: Gravity-assisted shoulder mobilization exercise using body weight for gentle movement
EX_544.instructions: Lean over table, let arm hang, gently swing in circles and pendulum motions

EX_545.name: Passive Shoulder Flexion
EX_545.description: Assisted shoulder flexion movement to maintain range of motion
EX_545.instructions: Use unaffected arm to lift affected arm overhead in pain-free range

EX_546.name: Cross-body Stretch
EX_546.description: Horizontal adduction stretch targeting posterior shoulder structures
EX_546.instructions: Pull affected arm across body with opposite hand, hold stretch

EX_547.name: Isometric Biceps Contractions
EX_547.description: Static muscle contraction without joint movement for early strengthening
EX_547.instructions: Contract biceps muscle against immovable object, hold contraction

EX_548.name: Eccentric Biceps Curls
EX_548.description: Controlled lowering phase of biceps curl for tendon remodeling
EX_548.instructions: Slowly lower weight over 3-5 seconds, assist with concentric phase

EX_549.name: Resisted Shoulder Flexion
EX_549.description: Progressive resistance training for shoulder flexors
EX_549.instructions: Pull theraband upward with straight arm, control return

EX_550.name: Scapular Stabilization
EX_550.description: Dynamic stabilization exercises for scapular control
EX_550.instructions: Perform scapular retraction and protraction with resistance

EX_551.name: Progressive Weight Training
